{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_InitPhoenixPL2}}
'''A_InitPhoenixPL2'''<br>
(''no parameter'')<br>

Sets the calling weapon's <tt>FlameCount</tt> field to 350, as long as this weapon is derived from {{Class|PhoenixRod}}. This is useless by itself and is meant to be used in conjunction with [[A_FirePhoenixPL2]].

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|PhoenixRodPowered}} and derived classes.

